                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝssar “Synaxarion” for the first four months of the year (fols.
                     2ra-253v)
 I-1) Maskaram (fols. 2ra-63rc)
 I-2) Ṭǝqǝmt (fols.
                     64ra-117vc)
 I-3) Ḫǝdār (fols. 118ra-180vc) 
 I-4) Tāḫśāś (fols.
                     181ra-253vc)
 The commemoration notes are followed by ʿarke-hymns
                     
 Additio 1.</summary>
