                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; names of the donors; four groups of
                           lines on the incipit page of each month, alternating with black lines;
                           two lines in the incipit of the first commemorative notice of the day;
                           one line (or the first word, as in fol. 30rb) in the incipit of the other
                           commemorative notices of the day; the first word of each ʿarke-hymn;
                           elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numbers.</seg>
                     </handNote>
